reviewerName: Jason P. Pumphrey "the movie & music man"
reviewText: I remember seeing this neat little made for TV gem in 1994,it was a great heist movie,Kenny Rogers plays the title role of MacShayne,an ex con who goes undercover in Vegas! It was nice to see it again in sparkling DVD quality + no commercials! The other stellar cast members include Barry Nelson,Ann Jillian and John Karlen! It was a TV movie,so don't expect it to be as extreme as other heist movies,but for what it is,its great entertainment! A+
summary: Kenny Rogers goes undercover as MacShayne!
